{
  "stem": "5639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when they matriculated in '32 and most of the boys pursued their own careers, my own brother went to France to study veterinary science.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My brother sent Leon-- Leon Drexler was his name-- for one year to France, so he, too, will know what it means to be a student.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he, too, will go overseas.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but not because he was so wealthy.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I mean--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but he, I am sure, that he approached some people for contributions because I know that many times people came to ask for contributions.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was not an unusual thing to collect money for a dowry.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If there was a poor girl, and the only thing that stopped her from getting married-- I'm sure there were other things that were stopping her, and the-- [LAUGHTER] The dowry was the dangling candy.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They collected for the dowry.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many times I remember that the wedding took place in my grandmother's apartment.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Complete strangers.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think it--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--came down-- I think it came down in my genes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember that I acquired these things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I never knew anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I never knew anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There is always this tradition that you have to do things from which others benefit, not for benefit for yourself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, that was part of my culture, of my upbringing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, when I think about it, it must have come with my genes, the same way as my hair and my eyes came.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were very close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And also, I don't know whether the proximity of Germany was a very contributing factor, but my father was a great admirer of Germans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a Germanophile.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
